OL,12,Fsaid it is unfair for those individuals
OL,13,Fto have to pay the #1,330
OL,14,Fnaturalisation charge.
OL,16,FThe committee said the policy ignored
OL,17,Fthe UK and Ireland's unique
OL,18,Frelationship.
